data.description: Fantastic home located is a quiet neighborhood yet just minutes to rt 3 , shopping and the town center ! The first floor offers an updated bathroom complete with a walk-in shower. Off the dining area you will be delighted by the beautiful 3 season porch with cathedral ceiling and access out to the deck. The lower level offers a front to back family room with daylight windows, a fireplace plus a half bath. Off the family room you will find a convenient office or great space if you want a 4th bedroom. Updated heating and central air system!  Young roof!  Clear overgrown brush in rear if you wish to expand your backyard , or enjoy less to mow.  With cosmetic work this is a great opportunity to purchase in an area of more expensive homes and build immediate equity! Easy to show and ready for a quick closing, book your appointment today!
